description: Bringing New Orleans style Snoballs to New England!! We start the tastiest treat you've had by shaving blocks of crystal clear ice with our special machines, down to delicious snow. Then we add our toppings to the snowball of your choice! Sour spray, marshmallow fluff, chocolate cream, and sweetened condensed milk are just a few of the toppings we can add to make your Snowball perfect!!! Come try our Snowballs today, and taste what you've been missing!
name: The Big Freezy
